panels.description: The main dashboard of PadoGrid Hazelcast Dashboards (PHD) that resembles the main dashboard of Hazelcast Management Center (HMC). PHD includes additional metrics that are not available in HMC and vice versa. PHD exposes a finer degree of individual metric details that are more suitable for monitoring production systems. HMC is suitable for production, development, and testing. It includes controls for managing cluster members and additional metrics obtained by directly connecting to Hazelcast members.
